import { gql } from "@apollo/client";

export const CREATE_USER = gql`
    mutation createUser(
            $username: String
            $email: String
            $password: String
            $firstName: String
            $lastName: String
            $created: String
            $isActive: Boolean
        ) {
            createUser(
                firstName: $firstName
                lastName: $lastName
                username: $username
                password: $password
                email: $email
                created: $created
                isActive: $isActive
            ) {
                id
                username
                lastName
                firstName
                created
                email
                isActive
            }
        }
    
`

export const CREATE_REVIEW = gql`
    mutation createReview(
            $description: String
            $authorId: Integer
            $movieId: Integer
            $rating: float
            $created: String
        ) {
            createReview(
                description: $description
                authorId: $authorId
                movieId: $movieId
                rating: $rating
                created: $created
            ) {
                description
                authorId
                movieId
                rating
                created
                id
            }
        }
    
`
